sentences: Paul Nabor (26 January 1928 – 22 October 2014), born Alfonso Palacio, was a Garifuna singer and musician from Punta Gorda, Belize.
Nabor was born as Alfonso Palacio on 26 January 1928.
Although official sources list his place of birth as Stann Creek Town (now Dangriga), Nabor told Amandala in 2009 that he had been born in Punta Gorda, where he was a lifelong resident.

He retired from performing full-time in 2009, but played occasionally until 2013.
